Q: Where are 3rd party library installed?
They are installed in ~/sketchbook/libraries
$ tree libraries/
libraries/
└── openkinect
    ├── examples
    │   ├── AveragePointTracking
    │   │   ├── AveragePointTracking.pde
    │   │   └── KinectTracker.pde
    │   ├── PointCloud
    │   │   ├── PointCloud.pde
    │   │   └── sketch.properties
    │   └── RGBDepthTest
    │       └── RGBDepthTest.pde
    ├── library
    │   ├── libKinect.jnilib
    │   └── openkinect.jar
    └── library.properties
!!! Examples are available in the example section under Contributed Libraries/OpenKinect

